This Mod Adds All The Skintones And Eye Colors Of The Human Race To The Races Mentioned In The Long Description.
It Does Not Change Anything.
It Only Affects The Race Menu.
descriptionHtml:
The Huminator

This Mod Adds All The Skintones And Eye Colors Of The Human Race To The Following Races:

Dark Elves
High Elves
Wood Elves
Orc

It Does Not Change Anything.
It Only Affects The Race Menu.

How To Install: Put The File In The Skyrim Data Folder.
author: JP0005
